      .row.meetups
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-1
          h3 I'm proud to be part of a tight-knit community of developers here in Nashville. Thanks to #[a(href="http://nashvillesoftwareschool.com/") Nashville Software School], #[a(href="http://www.meetup.com/nashjs/") Nash JS], and #[a(href="http://www.codefornashville.org/") Code For Nashville] for being great mentors and teachers.
